Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lambat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu terlambat sepuluh menit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti akan mati kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lupakan saja.\NMarie, masuk ke mobil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur tidak marah.\NBagaimana mungkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, selamat ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ulang tahun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini hari penting bagi orang yang kucintai,\Ntapi aku tak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ulang tahunku,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari 365 hari dalam setahun,\Nitu hari yang paling kubenci
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak orang menjadikan ulang tahunku\Nalasan untuk mengirim banyak hadiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, tersembunyi di dalamnya\Nada pisau atau bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanan di hari ulang tahunku\Nselalu diracuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pesta ulang tahunku selalu dibatalkan\Nkarena ancaman bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, di hari ulang tahunku,\Nada kenangan yang tak mau kuingat lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak apa-apa, tak perlu membahas itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu-satunya kenangan indah yang kumiliki
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah tahun aku datang ke rumah ini\Nsebagai anak tiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahku yang sibuk mengambil cuti kerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami berdua\Nmakan kue ulang tahun bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin hanya itu waktunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kue ulang tahun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum aku hidup dalam kemiskinan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seseorang membelikannya untukku\Nsetiap tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dulu sangat bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kembali ke rumah,\Naku juga akan membuat kue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena ulang tahun seharusnya
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menjadi hari yang bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terimalah hadiah ulang tahunku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Prinsipku adalah tak menerima\Nhadiah dari teman sekelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf.\NTolong ambil kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, tolong kembalikan semuanya untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa kita bicara sepulang sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mau berhubungan baik dengan kami,\NKlub Penggemar Tuan Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penggemar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami punya nama lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Klub yang Mau Tuan Arthur Melihat Mereka\Nsebagai Sampah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur sangat membenci manusia\Ndari lubuk hatinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kami menyapanya,\Ndia tak bisa tak memberi kami
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}senyuman canggung, tapi sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ekspresi resah itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menyukainya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah mengatakan semua itu,\Nentah apa kamu mengerti perasaan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, tolong urus ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa bertanya ke Tuan Arthur\Nuntuk kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, benarkah kamu mau kita akur?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku juga\Nsangat menyukai Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Mungkinkah kamu orang seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kuberi tahu ini di awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di klub penggemar kami, dosa besar\Njika menjadi "penggemar yang jatuh cinta".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tanya kenapa?\NItu karena Tuan Arthur terlalu sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jatuh cinta dengan orang terhormat\Nberarti melupakan posisimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya kamu menyerah saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kamu mau melawan kami, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo maju!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya jadi begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salahkah jika jatuh cinta\Ndengan Tuan Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kalian terlalu terbawa suasana,\Nseseorang bisa terluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, kami akan pergi sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, apa yang terjadi?\NKamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baik-baik saja.\NKami hanya bermain petak umpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.\NBaguslah kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ada tugas OSIS hari ini,\Njadi akan pulang terlambat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kamu pulang lebih dulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, jika aku memasukkan\Nbanyak makanan lezat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seharusnya tak apa-apa, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kejam sekali.\NJangan seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lengan kiriku belum sepenuhnya pulih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa menurut.\NOrang yang ingin membunuh Tuan Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang aku tak mau melakukan pembunuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan menyakiti Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, apa yang kamu lakukan di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah sudah jelas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri aku kue itu juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kue ulang tahun Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan menghalangiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, biar kuberi nasihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memasak adalah kesempatan bagus\Nuntuk menyingkirkan targetmu dari dalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pastikan kamu menyelesaikannya dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kueku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bau aneh apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku tak melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja, kamu tak pandai memasak, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berniat mengambil kue itu,\Ntapi tidak jadi karena tak menggugah selera.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, semangat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kejar cinta sepihakmu itu\Ndengan segenap kemampuanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetap saja, sistem keamanan rumah ini\Nsangat lemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan kembali dan melihat Marie\Nberpakaian pelayan lagi kapan-kapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengeluarkan kapak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Individu berbahaya terdeteksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cincang dia langsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadikan dia steik hamburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika Marie-2 ada di sini,\Nsebaiknya aku tidak datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saatnya kabur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sistem keamanan yang nonaktif berhasil\Ndiaktifkan kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meningkatkan prosedur patroli.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski ini cukup berbeda dari rencana awal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jika aku membungkusnya,\Nini masih terlihat layak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mode kekuatan penuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuenya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Maafkan aku...\N- Tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya, itu tak terlalu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, lanjutkan saja patrolinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak boleh memberikan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}...adalah melupakan posisimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kejarlah cinta sepihakmu itu\Ndengan segenap kemampuanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, meski aku membuat hadiah itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku masih tak tahu\Napa dia akan menerimanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, hasil buatanku buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sama sekali tak cocok\Ndengan Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alih-alih meninggalkan kenangan memalukan,\Nlebih baik tak memberikannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sedang apa, Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang, Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat lelah hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merepotkan sekali menolak semua hadiah\Nyang dikirim sepulang sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa lebih baik\Nmenerima kebaikan orang lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berdasarkan pengalamanku sebelumnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:10:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sangat sulit bagiku\Nuntuk memercayai orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya, hari seperti ini\Nbelum tentu hari baik bagi semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku benci ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ulang tahun seharusnya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hari yang bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku berharap\NTuan Arthur tak membenci hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat ulang tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekalipun kamu membenci hari ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tetap mau merayakannya bersamamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku mengunduh satu resep
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mencoba membuat ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak perlu lagi merasa depresi\Nkarena ulang tahunku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku memilikimu, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menemanimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan selalu berada di sini,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tepat di sisimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie menambahkan garam alih-alih gula.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sesuatu yang sudah lama\Nmau kulakukan untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakailah gaun ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh kubuka pintunya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, silakan masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf mengganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, pakaian apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sangat cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedikit lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangan Tuan Arthur terampil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kamu selalu di sisiku,\Nmengurus semuanya untukku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat memalukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Marie,\Nkamu tak perlu melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski dia melakukan banyak hal\Nuntuk membuatku bahagia,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kenapa aku masih merasa berat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak hadiah sudah tiba\Nuntuk Anda, Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu aku di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira aku sudah menyuruhmu\Nmeninggalkan semua hadiahku di luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu orang baru di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Persetan dengan ulang tahunmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang giliranku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah belajar,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kumodifikasi ini untuk menjatuhkan orang\Ndengan satu serangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, biasanya, itu aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membalaskan dendam rekan-rekanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa tunggu sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menunggu dengan patuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kenapa hatiku terasa berat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena alih-alih dilindungi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku, Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau melindungi Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, kamu luar biasa\Ndan mampu melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin sebelum aku datang,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu pasti menangkis para pembunuh itu\Nsendirian, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, karena kamu sangat kuat,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mau melindungimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak suka dilindungi olehku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku suka dilindungi oleh Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bilang Tuan Arthur pingsan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah menghubungi UKS?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum, tapi dia mau\Nkami segera menjemputmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bersumpah\Nakan melindungi Tuan Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang di Klub Pencinta Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengenai kemampuan atletikmu\Nyang menakjubkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu membuatku bertanya-tanya apakah kamu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}robot yang dikembangkan\Nperusahaan Arthur, Zetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, dia mudah ditipu\Nuntuk datang ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah dia robot cacat\Ndengan desain cacat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kami sangat mau mempelajarimu.\NItu alasan kami mengundangmu ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Mengundang?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lebih seperti\Npenculikan dan penahanan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus segera kabur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, mari bongkar dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, lepaskan pakaiannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa di antara kita\Nyang pernah melepas pakaian wanita?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial! Beraninya mereka menjebak kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal hanya robot, kenapa didesain\Nbisa bikin orang merasa bersalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sungguh tak bisa melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang-orang ini bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika terus begini, ini tak akan berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya, kakiku memiliki\Nfungsi antigravitasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa melayang\Ntiga milimeter di atas tanah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa?\N- Mustahil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah itu sama\Ndengan yang terkenal itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat, spesifikasi yang sangat tinggi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kurasa mustahil memastikannya\Njika seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa turunkan aku dari papan dulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau melihatnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa itu bukan ide bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan melayang sungguhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah dia hanya melompat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Robot juga bisa berbohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kabur! Kejar dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia robot yang berbahaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan mengasihanimu lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari bongkar dia!\NTeman-Teman, ambil obeng kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seseorang, tolong selamatkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kalian sungguh otaku robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelacak GPS?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berani mengganggu penelitian kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie adalah milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan menyerahkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melindunginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yang mau melindungi Tuan Arthur,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia melindungiku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kembali, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baju dalamku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa membiarkan Tuan Arthur\Nmelihatku dalam kondisi menyedihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, apa ada yang rusak?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus segera memikirkan sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kamu?\NAku tak mengenalmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie hilang ingatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya mereka merusaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua data tentang aku hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Datanya hilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kamu lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kita mengirimnya untuk pemeliharaan,\Ndia akan diperbaiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, mari kirim...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mencari cara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan membuatnya ingat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kurasa kamu tidak ingat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sebenarnya kita punya\NTujuh Peraturan Rutinitas Mesra Harian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya pernyataan konyol itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari coba Tujuh Peraturan itu dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin itu akan membuatmu\Nmengingat sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan mengikuti\Nperaturan yang dia sebutkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu bilang ingatanku sudah kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peraturan nomor satu.\NPelukan selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peraturan nomor dua.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berpegangan tangan di perjalanan sekolah,\Njari saling bertautan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peraturan nomor tiga.\NMenyuapiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peraturan nomor empat.\NSaling menatap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peraturan nomor lima.\NBantal pangkuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peraturan nomor enam.\NTepuk kepala.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya sudah lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, akhirnya, peraturan nomor tujuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kamu menutup matamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai dugaan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini ciuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sungguh tidak ingat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu kehilangan semua ingatanmu denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama kontak fisik dengan Master Arthur,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"mode kekasih" terdeteksi\Ndalam pemrograman intiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah menganalisis mode kekasih,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}data mengenai Tuan Arthur\Nditemukan dan dipulihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu ingat, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, tak pernah ada
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Tujuh Peraturan Rutinitas Mesra Kita"\Ndi antara kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu paling benci saat orang berbohong,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kamu juga membohongi orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Sejujurnya,\Njika peraturan mesra itu nyata,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita bisa berpegangan tangan\Ndalam perjalanan pulang."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keduanya memikirkan\Nhal yang sama di hati mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SMA Carmia melawan SMA Perenia.\NIni festival olahraga gabungan tahunan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balap karung atau pertarungan kavaleri,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie akan habis-habisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daryl, teman dekat Tuan Arthur?
